// std.io - Input/Output functions for OmniLang
//
// Surface mirrors Go's fmt + bufio + io as closely as makes sense without
// goroutines, varargs, or Reader/Writer interfaces.
//
// IMPLEMENTATION STATUS:
// [IMPLEMENTED] (Runtime): print, println, eprint, eprintln, flush,
//    is_terminal, read_line, read_all, sprintf, parse_int, parse_float,
//    is_int, is_float
// [IMPLEMENTED] (OmniLang body): sprint, sprintln, prompt, read_lines,
//    read_int, read_float
// [PARTIAL] read_line_async (returns Promise but is synchronous)

